OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FFour of the six US soldiers killed in
OL,7,Fan Iranian drone strike in Kuwait on
OL,8,FSunday have been named by the US
OL,9,FDepartment of Defence.
OL,11,FThey have been named as Captain Cody
OL,12,FKhork, 35; Sergeant First Class Nicole
OL,13,FAmor, 39; Sergeant First Class Noah
OL,14,FTietjens, 42, and Sergeant Declan
OL,15,FCoady, 20.
OL,17,FTwo other soldiers killed in the
OL,18,Fattack have not yet been publicly
OL,19,Fnamed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
