CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FThey were the first Americans to die
OL,7,Fin the war with Iran when they were
OL,8,Fkilled a day after the US and Israel
OL,9,Flaunched their military campaign
OL,10,Fagainst Tehran, when an "unmanned
OL,11,Faircraft system" hit a makeshift
OL,12,Foperations centre in Shuaiba port,
OL,13,FKuwait.
OL,15,FThe US Department of Defence said the
OL,16,Fincident is under investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
