OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FThe soldiers were members of the Army
OL,7,FReserve, assigned to the 103rd
OL,8,FSustainment Command, which provides
OL,9,Ffood, fuel, water, ammunition,
OL,10,Ftransport equipment and supplies.
OL,12,F"These men and women all bravely
OL,13,Fvolunteered to defend our country, and
OL,14,Ftheir sacrifice will never be
OL,15,Fforgotten," Army Secretary Daniel
OL,16,FDriscoll said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
