OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said "there
OL,7,Fwill likely be more" deaths of US
OL,8,Fsoldiers when he addressed the deaths
OL,9,Fon Sunday. "That's how it is", he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FHere is what we know about the US
OL,13,Fservice members who were killed on
OL,14,FSunday.
OL,16,FCaptain Cody Khork
OL,18,FKhork, from Lakeland, Florida, was
OL,19,Fvery patriotic and drawn to serving in
OL,20,Fthe US military from a young age, his
OL,21,Ffamily said in a statement on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
