OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FHe enlisted in the National Guard in
OL,7,F2009. He commissioned as a military
OL,8,Fpolice officer in the Army Reserve in
OL,9,F2014 and deployed to Saudi Arabia,
OL,10,FGuantanamo Bay, Cuba, and Poland.
OL,12,FBehind his sense of duty was "a man
OL,13,Fwhose life was defined by devotion,
OL,14,Fcharacter, and service," his parents
OL,15,Fand stepmother said.
OL,26,@tD@^OUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
