OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,F"Cody was truly the life of the party,
OL,7,Fknown for his infectious spirit,
OL,8,Fgenerous heart, and deep care for
OL,9,Fthose who served alongside him and for
OL,10,Feveryone blessed to know him," the
OL,11,Fstatement said.
OL,13,FKhork loved history and had a degree
OL,14,Fin political science, which showed
OL,15,F"his sharp mind and his sincere
OL,16,Fappreciation for the principles and
OL,17,Fsacrifices that have shaped our
OL,18,Fnation," they added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]wD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
