OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FOne of Khork's friends, Abbas Jaffer,
OL,7,Fposted on Facebook on Monday that he
OL,8,Fhad lost the best person he had ever
OL,9,Fknown.
OL,11,F"My best friend, best man, and brother
OL,12,Fgave his life defending our country
OL,13,Foverseas," Jaffer said. Khork and
OL,14,FJaffer had been friends for more than
OL,15,F16 years.
OL,17,FHis awards and decorations include the
OL,18,FMeritorious Service Medal, Army
OL,19,FCommendation Medal and Joint Service
OL,20,FAchievement Medal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
