OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FSergeant First Class Nicole Amor
OL,8,FAmor, from White Bear Lake, Minnesota,
OL,9,Fwas just days away from returning home
OL,10,Fto her husband and two children when
OL,11,Fthe attack struck.
OL,13,F"She was almost home," her husband,
OL,14,FJoey Amor, said on Tuesday to the
OL,15,FAssociated Press. "You don't go to
OL,16,FKuwait thinking something's going to
OL,17,Fhappen, and for her to be one of the
OL,18,Ffirst ` it hurts."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@VO]wD@SOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
