OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FHer husband said he last spoke to his
OL,7,Fwife two hours before she was killed.
OL,8,FHe said she was working long shifts,
OL,9,Fand they had been messaging about her
OL,10,Ftripping and falling the night before.
OL,11,F"She just never responded in the
OL,12,Fmorning," he said.
OL,14,FA week before the attack, Amor was
OL,15,Fmoved off-base to a shipping container-
OL,16,Fstyle building with no defences, Joey
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
