OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,F"They were dispersing because they
OL,7,Fwere in fear that the base they were
OL,8,Fon was going to get attacked, and they
OL,9,Ffelt it was safer in smaller groups in
OL,10,Fseparate places."
OL,12,FAmor was an avid gardener who enjoyed
OL,13,Fmaking salsa from the peppers and
OL,14,Ftomatoes in her garden with her son,
OL,15,Fwho is in his last year of high
OL,16,Fschool. She also enjoyed rollerblading
OL,17,Fand bicycling with her fourth-grade
OL,18,Fdaughter.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
