OL,6,FShe enlisted in the National Guard in
OL,7,F2005, transferred to the Army Reserve
OL,8,Fa year later, and deployed to Kuwait
OL,9,Fand Iraq in 2019.
OL,11,FAmor's decorations included the Army
OL,12,FCommendation Medal, National Defence
OL,13,FService Medal and Army Reserve
OL,14,FComponent Achievement Medal.
