OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FTietjens from Bellevue, Nebraska, was
OL,7,Fa prominent member of a martial arts
OL,8,Fstudio, which he attended along with
OL,9,Fhis wife and son. He earned a black
OL,10,Fbelt in Taekwondo and was also an
OL,11,Finstructor, according to a tribute
OL,12,Fposted by his studio.
OL,14,F"He did not simply wear a Black Belt,
OL,15,Fhe lived it," Martial Arts
OL,16,FInternational said in the post,
OL,17,Fpraising Tietjens as "a devoted
OL,18,Fhusband and father." The studio said a
OL,19,Fcollege fund has been established for
OL,20,FTietjens' son.
OL,26,@wD@MO]zD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
