OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FOn the mat and as a soldier, "he
OL,7,Fcarried the same values: honour,
OL,8,Fdiscipline, service, and commitment to
OL,9,Fothers," the organisation said.
OL,11,FThe Philippine Martial Arts Alliance
OL,12,Falso paid tribute to Tietjens, saying
OL,13,Fhe was "an instructor who gave his
OL,14,Ftime, discipline, and leadership to
OL,15,Fothers".
OL,17,FOne of his fellow soldiers said
OL,18,FTietjens was "the kind of guy that was
OL,19,Falways around to help you".
OL,26,@nD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
