OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772644279
OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FArmy Staff Sgt. Jonn Coleman, a fellow
OL,7,FNebraska soldier, said Tietjens'
OL,8,Fmentorship was the reason he was able
OL,9,Fto advance his military career,
OL,10,Fsaying, "he made you feel important.
OL,11,FAnd that's hard to find sometimes in
OL,12,Fthe military."
OL,14,F"He took me under his wing and got me
OL,15,Fto where I needed to be."
OL,17,FTietjens enlisted in the Army Reserve
OL,18,Fin 2006 as a wheeled vehicle mechanic.
OL,19,FHe had deployed to Kuwait twice
OL,20,Fbefore, in 2009 and 2019.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@YO]
