OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FNebraska Governor Jim Pillen paid
OL,7,Ftribute to the family on Tuesday.
OL,9,F"Noah stepped up to serve and defend
OL,10,Fthe American people from foreign
OL,11,Fenemies around the world ` a sacrifice
OL,12,Fwe must never forget," he wrote.
OL,14,F"We are holding the Tietjens family
OL,15,Fclose in our hearts during this
OL,16,Funbelievably difficult time and will
OL,17,Fkeep them in our prayers," he said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
