OL,6,FTietjens' awards and decorations also
OL,7,Finclude the Meritorious Service Medal,
OL,8,FArmy Commendation Medal and Army
OL,9,FAchievement Medal.
OL,11,FSergeant Declan Coady
OL,13,FCoady, from Des Moines, Iowa, had just
OL,14,Ftold his father before the war started
OL,15,Fthat he had been recommended for a
OL,16,Fpromotion from specialist to sergeant,
OL,17,Fa rank he was posthumously awarded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
