OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FHe was one of the youngest people in
OL,7,Fhis class but seemed to impress his
OL,8,Finstructors, his father Andrew Coady
OL,9,Fsaid Tuesday.
OL,11,F"He was very good at what he did," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I still don't fully think it's real,"
OL,15,Fhis sister Keira Coady said. "I just
OL,16,Fremember all of our conversations
OL,17,Fabout what he was going to do when he
OL,18,Fcame back."
