OL,3,CFour US soldiers killed in first days
OL,4,Cof Iran war named
OL,6,FCoady enlisted in the Army Reserve in
OL,7,F2023, where he trained as an
OL,8,Finformation technology specialist
OL,9,Fwhile also studying cybersecurity at
OL,10,FDrake University in Des Moines. He was
OL,11,Ftaking online classes while in Kuwait
OL,12,Fand wanted to become an officer.
OL,14,FIowa Governor Kim Reynolds honoured
OL,15,FCoady for his service, saying in a
OL,16,Fstatement he "heroically answered his
OL,17,Fnation's call to duty and gave the
OL,18,Fultimate sacrifice."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
